description: Lists the access policies associated with an access entry.

parameters.name: principalArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the IAM principal for the AccessEntry.

parameters.name: nextToken
parameters.description: The nextToken value returned from a previous paginated request, where maxResults was used and the results exceeded the value of that parameter. Pagination continues from the end of the previous results that returned the nextToken value. This value is null when there are no more results to return.

nested_items.name: principalArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the IAM principal for the AccessEntry.

nested_items.description: The nextToken value returned from a previous paginated request, where maxResults was used and the results exceeded the value of that parameter. Pagination continues from the end of the previous results that returned the nextToken value. This value is null when there are no more results to return.

nested_items.name: associatedAccessPolicies
nested_items.description: The list of access policies associated with the access entry.

nested_items.name: accessScope
nested_items.description: The scope of the access policy.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: The scope type of an access policy.

nested_items.name: namespaces
nested_items.description: A Kubernetes namespace that an access policy is scoped to. A value is required if you specified namespace for Type.

nested_items.name: associatedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time the AccessPolicy was associated with an AccessEntry.

nested_items.name: modifiedAt
nested_items.description: The Unix epoch timestamp for the last modification to the object.
